workout_journal.title: Morning Yoga Routine
workout_journal.body: Started the day with a refreshing 30-minute yoga session focusing on flexibility and mindfulness. Felt energized and ready to tackle the day.

workout_journal.title: Evening Run in the Park
workout_journal.body: Completed a 5 km run in the local park. The weather was perfect and I managed to beat my previous time. Feeling accomplished and motivated.

workout_recipe.title: High-Protein Chicken Salad
workout_recipe.body: Grilled chicken breast diced and mixed with quinoa, cherry tomatoes, cucumber, and avocado. Seasoned with lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and pepper. Perfect for a post-workout meal to aid muscle recovery.

workout_recipe.title: Energizing Smoothie Bowl
workout_recipe.body: Blend together bananas, blueberries, and spinach with a scoop of protein powder. Top with chia seeds, sliced almonds, and a drizzle of honey. Great for an energy boost before a workout.

workout_recipe.title: Quinoa and Black Bean Salad
workout_recipe.body: Cooked quinoa mixed with black beans, corn, bell peppers, and cilantro. Tossed in a lime vinaigrette. A balanced meal to provide sustained energy for endurance workouts.
